    "en": "Saint Adrian of Canterbury, Abbot"
  },
  "collect": {
    "body": {
      "plain": {
        "en": "O Father of mercy, who called Saint Adrian to follow the Lord as a monk and a missionary; grant, we beseech you, that we may be filled with the same faith and zeal, and walk always as children of the light. Through our Lord Jesus Christ, your Son, who lives and reigns with you in the unity of the Holy Spirit, one God, for ever and ever."
      },
